customMethods.name: getReservationActivity
customMethods.script:
# Comment: ORDER BY ISNULL([Reservation].[timeRetired], [Reservation].[timeCreated]) desc means that 
	# activities should be ordered chronologicaly by 2 columns timeRetired and timeCreated
	
	query = """				
SELECT TOP(50)
	CONCAT_WS(' ',[Human].[firstName],[Human].[middleName],[Human].[lastName]) AS participantName
	,[Reservation].[timeCreated]
	,[Reservation].[timeRetired]
	,[Reservation].[reservationStart]
	,[Reservation].[reservationEnd]
	,[Room].[roomName]
	,[Bed].[bedName]
	,[Reservation].[notes]
	,[Program].[programName]
FROM [RitiOps].[lodging].[Reservation] 
	LEFT JOIN [RITIOps].[shelter].[WaitList] ON [Reservation].[participantId] = [WaitList].[participantid] AND [Reservation].[timeCreated] >= [WaitList].[dateadded] AND [Reservation].[timeCreated] <= [WaitList].[dateremoved]
	INNER JOIN [RITIOps].[shelter].[WaitListPrograms] ON [WaitListPrograms].[id] = [WaitList].[WaitListProgramId]
	INNER JOIN [RITIOps].[interaction].[Program] ON [Program].[id] = [WaitListPrograms].[programId]
	INNER JOIN [RITIOps].[participant].[Participant] ON [Participant].[id] = [Reservation].[participantId] 
	INNER JOIN [RITIOps].[humans].[Human] ON [Participant].[humanId] = [Human].[id] 
	INNER JOIN [RitiOps].[lodging].[Bed] ON [Reservation].[bedId] = [Bed].[id]
	INNER JOIN [RitiOps].[lodging].[Room] ON [Bed].[roomId] = [Room].[id]
WHERE [Room].[facilityId] = ?

ORDER BY ISNULL([Reservation].[timeRetired], [Reservation].[timeCreated]) desc"""
	
	result = system.db.runPrepQuery(query,[facilityId],'RITIOps')
	
	pyds = system.dataset.toPyDataSet(result)
	
	caseList = []
	for item in pyds:
		caseDict = {}
		
		if item['timeRetired'] is None:
			_title = 'New Reservation'
			_date = item['timeCreated'] 
		else:
			_title = 'Deleted Reservation'
			_date = item['timeRetired']
		
		caseDict['Title'] = _title
		caseDict['Date'] = system.date.format(_date)
		caseDict['CardType'] = 'Reservation'
		
		caseDict['InfoList'] = []
		caseDict['InfoList'].append({'Label': 'Participant', 'Value': item['participantName']})
		caseDict['InfoList'].append({'Label': 'Waiting List', 'Value': item['programName']})
		caseDict['InfoList'].append({'Label': 'Created Date', 'Value': system.date.format(item['reservationStart'],'MMM. d, YYYY')})

		_date = system.date.format(item['reservationEnd'],'MMM. d, YYYY') if item['reservationEnd'] is not None else ''
		caseDict['InfoList'].append({'Label': 'Expiration Date', 'Value': _date})
		caseDict['InfoList'].append({'Label': 'Room', 'Value': item['roomName']})
		caseDict['InfoList'].append({'Label': 'Bed', 'Value': item['bedName']})
		#caseDict['InfoList'].append({'Label': 'Notes', 'Value': item['notes']})
		
		caseList.append(caseDict)
		
	return caseList

customMethods.name: XgetOccupationActivity
customMethods.script:
query = """		
SELECT TOP(5) 
CONCAT_WS(' ',[Human].[firstName],[Human].[middleName],[Human].[lastName]) AS participantName
	,[BedLog].[eventStart]
	,[BedLog].[eventEnd]
	,[Room].[roomName]
	,[Bed].[bedName]

FROM [RitiOps].[lodging].[BedLog]  
	INNER JOIN [RITIOps].[participant].[Participant] ON [Participant].[id] = [BedLog].[participantId] 
	INNER JOIN [RITIOps].[humans].[Human] ON [Participant].[humanId] = [Human].[id]
	INNER JOIN [RitiOps].[lodging].[Bed] ON [BedLog].[bedId] = [Bed].[id]
	INNER JOIN [RitiOps].[lodging].[Room] ON [Bed].[roomId] = [Room].[id] 
WHERE [Room].[facilityId] = ?
ORDER BY [BedLog].[id] desc"""
	
	result = system.db.runPrepQuery(query,[facilityId],'RITIOps')
	
	pyds = system.dataset.toPyDataSet(result)
	
	caseList = []
	for item in pyds:
		caseDict = {}
		
		if item['eventEnd'] is None:
			_title = 'Check-in'
			_date = item['eventStart']
			_dateHeader = 'Start Date'
		else:
			_title = 'Check-out'
			_date = item['eventEnd']
			_dateHeader = 'Check Out Date'
		
		caseDict['Title'] = _title
		caseDict['Date'] = _date
		caseDict['CardType'] = 'Occupation'
		
		caseDict['InfoList'] = []
		caseDict['InfoList'].append({'Label': 'Participant', 'Value': item['participantName']})
		caseDict['InfoList'].append({'Label': _dateHeader, 'Value':system.date.format(_date,'MMM. d, YYYY') })
		caseDict['InfoList'].append({'Label': 'Room', 'Value': item['roomName']})
		caseDict['InfoList'].append({'Label': 'Bed', 'Value': item['bedName']})
		
		
		caseList.append(caseDict)
		
	return caseList

customMethods.name: setJoined
customMethods.script:
emvFilter = self.getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("Filter_EmbeddedView")
	flex = self.getChild("FlexRepeater")
	
	try:
		facilityId = long(self.view.params.facilityId)
	except:
		system.perspective.print(('facilityId is not number!'))
		facilityId = -1


	if facilityId <= 0:
		flex.props.instances = []
		return
		
	instanceList = []
	jsonBase = '''{
			"instanceStyle": {
			  "classes": "ActivityCards/Card"
			},
			"instancePosition": {
			  "grow": 0,
			  "shrink": 0
			}
	}'''
	
	selection = emvFilter.props.params.selection
	
	if not(selection):
		selection = ['All']
	
	flex.props.instances = []
	joined = []
	
	if 'All' in selection or 'Reservation' in selection:
		joined = joined + self.getReservationActivity(facilityId)
		
	if 'All' in selection or 'Check-In' in selection:
		joined = joined + self.getCheckInActivity(facilityId)
	
	if 'All' in selection or 'Check-Out' in selection: 
		joined = joined + self.getCheckOutActivity(facilityId)
	
	# sort descending by Date value in dictionary 
	joinedSorted = sorted(joined, key = lambda i: i['Date'],reverse=True)

	#ystem.perspective.print(('joinedSorted1:',joinedSorted))
	
	# Leave only last 50 activities to display inside views.
	joinedSorted = joinedSorted[:50]
	
	ln = len(joinedSorted)
	
	auxList = []
	for i in range(ln):
		month = system.date.format(system.date.parse(joinedSorted[i-1]['Date']), 'yyyyMM') if i>0 else '000000'
		monthNext = system.date.format(system.date.parse(joinedSorted[i]['Date']), 'yyyyMM')
		
		#ystem.perspective.print((i,month, monthNext))
		if i == 0 or month != monthNext:
			auxList.append({'Date': joinedSorted[i]['Date'], 'CardType': 'MonthYear', "Title": "","InfoList": []}) # pass 
		auxList.append(joinedSorted[i])		

	#system.perspective.print(('joinedSorted2:',auxList))
	
	for activity in auxList: #joinedSorted:
		auxDict= system.util.jsonDecode(jsonBase)
		auxDict['OneCase'] = activity
		auxDict['Size'] = ''
		instanceList.append(auxDict)
	
	flex.props.instances = instanceList
	
	#system.perspective.print(('self.getReservationActivity(facilityId):',self.getReservationActivity(facilityId)))
	#system.perspective.print(('self.getCheckInActivity(facilityId):',self.getCheckInActivity(facilityId)))
	#system.perspective.print(('self.getCheckOutActivity(facilityId):',self.getCheckOutActivity(facilityId)))
